Configures Port 0 pins as output using IODIR0

Turns all LEDs OFF initially using IOSET0

Blinks LEDs connected to even-numbered bits (0, 2, 4, 6)

Uses IOCLR0 (active low) to turn LEDs ON

Uses IOSET0 to turn LEDs OFF

Simple loop-based LED pattern with a delay

